##Can China, the world's factory, export masks, warming guns and alcohol as overseas orders surge?

“

At present, it seems that in the epidemic prevention material sequence, the production capacity is sufficient, the ability to supply overseas markets, may be alcohol disinfection products.

”

With the spread of new Crown Disease in the world, the supply of epidemic prevention and control materials such as protection, elimination and so on is still tight. Global supply demand is expected to increase by 40 percent, personal protective equipment reported on March 4.

World Health Organization (WHO) director-general Tan Desai said at a press conference at the Geneva headquarters on March 3 local time that in response to the new crown disease, the WHO estimates that 89 million surgical masks, 76 million pairs of inspection gloves and 1.6 million pairs of goggles are needed worldwide each month.

As the earliest outbreak area, China's demand for epidemic prevention and control materials is still huge, domestic production of related materials is still focused on the supply of domestic demand.

The medical mask is one of the most scarce epidemic prevention and control products after this outbreak. But with the industrial chain upstream and downstream enterprises gradually resume work, more enterprises to the production mask, production capacity to recover and growth. On March 2, the National Development and Reform Commission revealed that the daily production capacity and output of face masks in China have exceeded 100 million, further easing the contradiction between supply and demand.

Even so, it is not easy for individual consumers to buy medical masks. According to the interface news, most of the production capacity of mask manufacturers are still subject to national allocation, first of all to protect medical and epidemic prevention and control first-line personnel needs.

Taking Shandong Rizhao Sanqi Medical Products Co. , Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as "Sanqi Medical") as an example, this company has been producing masks since 1993, and the mask single product industry and technical level are in the forefront of the industry internationally, exports of face masks and protective clothing have been the main business in the past, during the fight against SARS, avian influenza and other epidemics, but also for the epidemic area supply of medical products. After the outbreak of new pneumonia, the Ministry of Industry and Information Technology identified as the key production supply units, to supply the domestic market.

The production capacity of Sanqi medical has been greatly improved, with the daily production of face masks increasing from more than 500,000 to more than 1.5 million and the daily production of medical protective clothing increasing from more than 1,000 to more than 5,000, Xinhua reported on March 2. Che Jinjun, Deputy General Manager of the company, said a large number of products would be exported at this time in the past. Now to support the prevention and control of the domestic epidemic, the company and Foreign Coordination of all foreign trade orders, to supply domestic needs. Factory "people do not rest" , 24-hour full production, but also emergency overseas branches of the epidemic prevention supplies to domestic emergency.

An industry insider, who did not want to be named, told interface news that the supply of masks in circulation on the market is very limited, and the production capacity of most enterprises is subject to the deployment of the state. Although many mask factories were built after the outbreak of the disease, and many enterprises turned to make masks, the core material of medical masks produced by upstream suppliers was not enough, many mask factories in the "no rice under the POT" situation.

Another major epidemic prevention and control materials infrared thermometer supply is also very tight.

Previously, the Shanghai Securities News reported that the overseas orders of Dali Technology, a manufacturer of infrared thermal imaging body temperature detection equipment, had increased rapidly recently, but compared with the large-scale infrared thermal imaging body temperature detection equipment produced by Dali Technology, hand-held temperature measurement equipment (ear temperature gun, forehead temperature gun) market gap is larger.

According to statistics from the Medical Health Industry Research Center, the production of hand-held infrared thermometers in China was between 200,000 and 300,000 until 2019, and the overall market size is not large. And 2020 after the outbreak of new pneumonia, the amount of warm gun orders suddenly increased, a "hard to get a shot" situation. According to figures released by the Ministry of Industry and Information Technology in early February this year, the market gap for hand-held infrared thermometers is about 550,000.

Interface News in the interview found that hand-held temperature measurement equipment related to the current supply of products are also dominated by the domestic market.

Yuyue Medical Group and Jiu'an Medical Group are currently the leading manufacturers of infrared thermometers in China. Interface News saw on the investor interaction platform that when answering questions from investors about supply in overseas markets, all said that the current product supply exceeds demand, mainly to ensure domestic epidemic first-line demand.

According to information it has obtained on the open market, there are no more than three manufacturers in China that are capable of producing electronic thermometers, including mass production, and not many that are capable of large scale production increases, the company said. At present, there is still a gap in demand. Although the daily production capacity of the company has exceeded 10,000 units, it still can not meet the overall demand. The company is actively purchasing production-related equipment to expand production capacity, it aims to reach 15,000 units a day by early March. Although we have been receiving inquiries from Japan, South Korea, Italy, France, the United States, Germany and other places, as a Chinese company, will give priority to the protection of domestic public health and epidemic prevention needs. If the domestic epidemic situation is improved, we will give priority to the domestic public health and epidemic prevention needs, under the premise of considering the supply of warm guns and related fields of medical equipment to foreign areas.

Interface news called ULIDE technology (China) Co. , a large manufacturer of infrared thermometers, and learned that the company had run out of infrared thermometers since January because parts from upstream manufacturers were in short supply, we are unable to take orders at this time.

For now, it seems likely that alcohol-based disinfectants have sufficient capacity in the pipeline to supply overseas markets.

SDIC bio-tech Investment Co. , China's largest producer of ethanol by capacity, has signed an export interest order of about 100 tons, securities daily reported recently.

In an interview with the Securities Daily, Yue Guojun, chief scientist of the SDIC group and Chairman of the Board of SDIC biology, said, "China is the world's second-largest producer of alcohol, and we can rest assured that our production capacity is not an issue to ensure the supply of alcohol disinfectants. "The reason why there was once a regional shortage of alcohol disinfectant was mainly because the demand for alcohol disinfectant rose too quickly after the outbreak of the epidemic, coupled with the fact that it was just in time for the Spring Festival, many manufacturers were on holiday and the logistics were blocked, resulting in a sudden gap between supply and demand. "

According to Him, China's total ethanol production capacity is about 15 million tons per year, and the production capacity for producing alcohol disinfectant is about 9 million tons per year. Among them, Sdic bio-ethanol annual production capacity of 1.6 million tons, the largest in China. Currently, SDIC's five alcohol production bases in Meihekou City, Jilin City, Yushu, Tieling, Liaoning Province, and Zhanjiang, Guangdong Province, have rapidly switched to producing alcohol disinfectants that meet national standards, has achieved the daily production of alcohol disinfectant capacity of 2000 tons, according to market demand supply capacity can be further enhanced.

Regarding overseas orders, sdic biology also told interface news that "since production capacity is not a problem, it can take care of both domestic and overseas markets. ".

But not all alcohol producers have started to supply overseas markets.

COFCO'S COFCO Biotechnology Co. , Ltd. (COFCO) is one of the leading domestic alcohol suppliers, with a current production capacity of more than 1,000 tons per day. Interface reporter as a dealer to contact cofco biology, the latter said that currently do not accept overseas orders.

According to Shandong Weigao Group, which produces alcohol and protective clothing, the group's anti-epidemic materials are still subject to the unified allocation of the state and do not supply to the market or take overseas orders.

The Ministry of Industry and Information Technology (MIIT) recently disclosed that on February 20, the daily output of 84 disinfectants, hands-free disinfectants and alcohol and other major disinfectants increased by 207% , 151% and 270% respectively compared with the end of January. Taking alcohol as an example, with the resumption of work in alcohol enterprises and the conversion of some former grain and wine factories and chemical factories, there is even a phenomenon of oversupply in some areas, and some enterprises have already started to reduce their production load due to large stocks.
